<!-- ðŸ§­ Project Overview -->
<h4 class="text-center mt-5">Project Overview</h4>
<p class="text-center my-4">
  The Chicago Historical Travel Assistant is a Streamlit app that allows users to query historical documents about Chicago. It uses PDF processing, natural language processing, and sentence-transformer embeddings to provide relevant historical context from uploaded PDFs. This tool demonstrates integrating AI with archival research to make historical knowledge easily accessible.
</p>

<div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
