  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
    {% include figure.liquid loading="eager" path="assets/projectimages/chicago-ai/query_example.png" title="Query Example" alt="User querying the app about the Chicago River reversal" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" style="height: 250px; object-fit: contain;" %}
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
    {% include figure.liquid loading="eager" path="assets/projectimages/chicago-ai/context_result.png" title="Result Context" alt="App displaying historical context from PDF" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" style="height: 250px; object-fit: contain;" %}
  </div>
</div>
<p class="caption text-center">
  The app retrieves relevant chunks of historical PDFs and displays them with relevance scoring, helping users explore Chicago's history interactively.
</p>

<!-- ðŸ–¼ï¸ AI Workflow -->
<h4 class="text-center mt-5">AI Workflow</h4>
<div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
  <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
    {% include figure.liquid loading="eager" path="assets/projectimages/chicago-ai/workflow.png" title="AI Workflow" alt="Diagram of PDF processing and NLP workflow" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" %}
  </div>
</div>
<p class="caption text-center">
  The workflow includes PDF text extraction, chunking, embedding via sentence-transformers, and context retrieval using a query interface built in Streamlit.
</p>

